title: Jake Paul Exposed By Bombshell New York Times Article - H3 After Dark # 33
description: On this episode of H3 After Dark Ethan, Hila and the gang talk about the new Jake Paul expose in the New York Times and speak to the article's author, Taylor Lorenz! We also talk about Benny Shapeeno's wood, Japanese social media stars using Face App to change genders, and a civil war breaks out amongst the crew over Ethan's wikifeet score coming close to being toppled!!!
